result.notes:
To quantify the rate of escape of commercially targeted fish underneath the 
ground gear and through the gaps between the fishing line and ground gear of 
the GOV trawl used in the North Sea groundfish survey (research vessel), and 
to calibrate the catch rates on the research vessel to commercial catch rates 
using commercial gear and practices on commercial vessels.
